# VASCO60 local catalog caches
#
# When set, the pipeline queries a local HEALPix-5 Parquet cache instead
# of making per-tile VizieR network calls. When unset, VizieR is used as
# before (no change in behaviour).
#
# To build a cache from scratch, see scripts/local_cache/<catalog>/README.md.
# To activate, copy this file to .env and uncomment the lines below.
# .env is gitignored.

# Gaia DR3 (60 GB, 1.81 B rows, ~35x speedup)
# VASCO_GAIA_CACHE=/Volumes/SANDISK/Gaia

# Pan-STARRS1 DR2 (311 GB, 10.56 B rows, ~262x speedup with nDet>=3 filter)
# VASCO_PS1_CACHE=/Volumes/SANDISK/PS1

# USNO-B1.0 (82 GB, 1.05 B rows, ~14x speedup)
# VASCO_USNOB_CACHE=/Volumes/SANDISK/USNOB
